Description:
    Explain the generator

Example:
    rails generate folio:component SomeThing

    This will create:
        app/models/project_namespace/some_thing.rb
        app/components/project_namespace/some_thing_component.rb
        app/components/project_namespace/some_thing/show.slim
        test/components/project_namespace/some_thing_component_test.rb

    rails generate folio:component /SomeThing

    This will create:
        app/models/some_thing.rb
        app/components/some_thing_component.rb
        app/components/some_thing/show.slim
        test/components/some_thing_component_test.rb
